a014350c71f9306a4af8295","tid":801422,"uid":72519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b2911613fd40f484caf6b3d9a2011bd2e17e476","tid":801422,"uid":134317,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T08:59:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i37.tinypic.com/2wcm9at.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi37.tinypic.com%2F2wcm9at.jpg&h=8c45ab6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T10:29:04.000Z","msg":"張凳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"983eeb9931351654595433dec385f1bf0b59f365","tid":801422,"uid":81443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"797a5639f07b5890d78c0eaffbd725e733e03668","tid":801422,"uid":179680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T15:17:11.000Z","msg":"開錯台 再開<br />\n<br />\n舊區紅van 基本上無鬼佬識搭 就算係鬼都要講廣東話<br />\n車頭用手寫牌 落車要大嗌 要自己記街名路線 <br />\n預備好銀仔 要找錢既前一個街口要俾定<br />\n上車即刻坐 唔好慢動作揀位<br />\n開咗門叫你上得即係有位 上到黎唔好仲成隻鴕鳥咁望<br />\n黃燈都會衝埋 唔會拘泥於小節<br />\n車程長有時會播經典歌 上次聽住鄧麗君全集返屋企 覺得司機好有深度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T10:29:21.000Z","msg":"街頭移動炸彈"},{"pid":"0a851545b3fbd44acd0d404f9dd1d2bf3024dd62","tid":801422,"uid":63491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T10:44:49.000Z","msg":"電車先有香港味道呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f1d20097c82ac7ac79e2605218e1432258c0604","tid":801422,"uid":179680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a851545b3fbd44acd0d404f9dd1d2bf3024dd62","tid":801422,"uid":63491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T10:44:49.000Z","msg":"電車先有香港味道呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T10:56:39.000Z","msg":"同意 不過只係住過港島短時間 無咩個人感受<br />\n但前排一條友由中環坐到筲箕灣來回去沈澱一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55565965e34a25ceb63793d021bb2853e89baa1e","tid":801422,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:02:21.000Z","msg":"上車無禁區<br />\n落車有禁區"},{"pid":"5ff6a1a8fd923fc3e459e076f700f063a2778044","tid":801422,"uid":193131,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老豆以前揸綠頂，但係揸到好似紅頂咁，因為係拆帳<br />\n其實而家都冇分綠定係紅頂快d，拆帳路線就快，月薪就hea揸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搭過一次老豆車，明明落斜轉緊灣都加速，以後唔敢再搭佢車"},{"pid":"e795d0468ecbb643700bacb559c32478454a775c","tid":801422,"uid":48582,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:08:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老豆以前揸綠頂，但係揸到好似紅頂咁，因為係拆帳<br />\n其實而家都冇分綠定係紅頂快d，拆帳路線就快，月薪就hea揸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搭過一次老豆車，明明落斜轉緊灣都加速，以後唔敢再搭佢車</blockquote><br />\n有啲月薪、但有編定班次嘅線都會飛得好快<br />\n快快手返站頭慢慢吹水煲煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f064409a051a1d74f148fdc7bfa64161933aef","tid":801422,"uid":21924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T13:24:01.000Z","msg":"住新界，唔識搭紅van"},{"pid":"19d18a57da2472c07cb9b4ed2a02bc8e0e0030d6","tid":801422,"uid":167219,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T13:55:54.000Z","msg":"有次凌晨搭青山道係旺角去長沙灣<br />\nDllm我上左車之後原來d乘客好快落哂車<br />\n沿路都冇客上<br />\n個師傅好似好燥咁<br />\n全程揸得快仲同d的士鏈車<br />\n你過我我過你<br />\n呢七分鐘我成世都記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}